<section class="w-full py-24 md:py-32 px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 bg-[#141617]">
  <div
    class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col order-2 lg:order-1 pr-0 lg:pr-10">
      <span
        class="text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.25em] text-[#3cbce6] uppercase mb-4"
      >
        Vision & Manifesto
      </span>
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8"
        style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
      >
        Designing for the<br class="hidden lg:block" /> Next Century
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-slate-400 text-[15px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] font-light mb-6"
      >
        We are not interested in fleeting trends. Our aim is to create work that
        possesses a timeless quality—structures and interfaces that will be as
        relevant in fifty years as they are today.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-slate-400 text-[15px] md:text-[17px] leading-[1.8] font-light mb-12"
      >
        The future belongs to spaces and digital realms that ground us, that
        offer a sanctuary from the relentless acceleration of modern life. This
        is our manifesto: to build the quiet landmarks of tomorrow.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/archive"
        class="group flex items-center gap-4 text-[10px] md:text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase hover:text-[#3cbce6] transition-colors w-fit pb-2 border-b border-white/20 hover:border-[#3cbce6]"
      >
        Explore Our Archives
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative w-full aspect-[4/5] lg:aspect-[4/5] order-1 lg:order-2 rounded-sm overflow-hidden"
    >
      <img
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop"
        alt="Futuristic architecture perspective"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
